data.description: Beautiful ranch style home on large corner lot was once model home in desired Lexington Village. Wonderful starter home or investment property! Formal living room with bay window, open kitchen/family floor plan with wood burning fireplace and vaulted ceilings. Home is filled with light. Spacious kitchen with abundance of cabinet space, stainless steel applinaces and granite countertops. Slider from family room leads to large fenced backyard perfect for pets and entertaining.  Laminate floor through out home. Master suite with private bath, 2 larger bedrooms. Newer AC unit, and fresh paint. [Home Energy Score = 5. HES Report at https://rpt.greenbuildingregistry.com/hes/OR10221330]
